==English==

===Pronunciation===
*:Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-ɪkt|-ɪkt]]

===Verb===
'''to restrict'''  ([[restricts]], [[restricted]], [[restricting]])
# To [[restrain]] [[within]] [[bound]]s; to limit; to [[confine]]; as, to restrict worlds to a particular meaning; to restrict a patient to a certain diet.

